User-Service
GetMapping
based on email - http://localhost:8181/user/email/akhila@gmail.com
based on id - http://localhost:8181/user/5
=====================================================
postMapping 
http://localhost:8181/user/register
json input

{
    "email": "pinky@gmail.com",
    "password":"pinky#04",
    "name":"pinky"
}
================================================
putMapping
updating name and password 
http://localhost:8181/user/5
json input

{
    "password":"pinky#04",
    "name":"pinky"
}
============================================
deleteMapping
http://localhost:8181/user/5
