MovieContentService
postMapping 
url-http://localhost:8181/movie/add
{
  "title": "Inception",
  "genre": "Sci-Fi",
  "language": "English",
  "description": "A dream within a dream",
  "videoUrl": "http://example.com/inception.mp4",
  "rating": 9.0,
  "thumbnailUrl": "http://example.com/inception.jpg"
}
================================
getmapping based on id -http://localhost:8181/movie/1
getmapping based on genre-http://localhost:8181/movie/genre/Sci-Fi
getting all movies - http://localhost:8181/movie
getmapping for search - http://localhost:8181/movie/search?title=Interstellar
